Projectify is project-management app for [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]], inspired by products like [[Todoist|https://todoist.com]] and [[Basecamp|https://basecamp.com]]. 

[[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com]] is an excellent note-taking & knowledge-base app with [[unique features|https://tiddlywiki.com/#TiddlyWiki]]. Projectify brings project managment to ~TiddlyWIki, transforming it into a complete digital second brain.

Projectify is carefully crafted, with attention to details. It is  evolving at a quick pace, soon reaching the version 1.0. Projectify is open-source, released under the MIT license.

For all changes in the latest {{$:/plugins/nico/projectify!!version}} release, see [[ChangeLog|$:/plugins/nico/projectify/changelog]].

